{"tid":2386360,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[冇圖]其實點解男同女既Appearance分別會咁大","createTime":"2021-01-29T13:50:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-01T05:12:57.000Z","uid":302151,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"23b14fd80062482bcc5f2e9bab4033e47fc47d66","tid":2386360,"uid":302151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T13:50:14.000Z","msg":"尋日唔小心睇到白雪公主劉馬車<br />\n除左好撚想嘔同好撚想洗眼之外<br />\n其實點解明明同一件衫 <br />\n女既著就又可愛又靚<br />\n男人著就會令人咁想嘔<br />\n<br />\n我講緊既Appearance好大分別 <br />\n唔只係講話有冇奶/J;屎忽淫唔淫賤;長唔長頭髮<br />\n其實男人同女人既&quot;樣,面型同骨架&quot;都係有好大分別  <br />\n但明明絕大部分既動物都要特登去睇佢有冇J/有冇奶先會知佢係男定女<br />\n<br />\n所以男人真係無論點都做唔到好似女仔咁可愛/咁靚(唔計極醜/極肥)<br />\n個啲咩日本偽娘睇相就可能呃到下人<br />\n但一拍片睇佢樣,面型同骨架就完全睇得出係男人 同埋個種可愛/靚既感覺都會即刻冇哂"},{"pid":"17434af775166e7ede0d0ce7d04685b50429348b","tid":2386360,"uid":35429,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T13:59:48.000Z","msg":"你點睇佢地兩個?<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HWRZFrlGxVs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DHWRZFrlGxVs&d=mGfgamXUORjeED7mKz2VH9Dxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=26e81987\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HWRZFrlGxVs</a>"},{"pid":"b1b90e4d08dc7e269a1d09aacf1a43232dbb50d8","tid":2386360,"uid":30831,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T14:14:01.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">但明明絕大部分既動物都要特登去睇佢有冇J/有冇奶先會知佢係男定女</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n你肯定？會唔會只係人類先唔明<br />\n如果唔係佢哋應該成日屌錯屎眼"},{"pid":"c1637f61ec9b299a6a1d87e5a0b220591d64a41a","tid":2386360,"uid":302151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"17434af775166e7ede0d0ce7d04685b50429348b","tid":2386360,"uid":35429,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T13:59:48.000Z","msg":"你點睇佢地兩個?<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HWRZFrlGxVs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DHWRZFrlGxVs&d=mGfgamXUORjeED7mKz2VH9Dxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h